// Cognition Layer Phase 6 — span writer.
//
// Every prompt invocation emits one or more spans through writeSpan().
// Spans never block the caller: persistence failures are logged and
// swallowed so a broken DB can't take down inference.
//
// Three backends, switched by LLM_TRACES_BACKEND env var:
//   memory (default)  — in-process ring buffer, capped at 10k spans
//   pg                — Postgres-backed via src/db pool
//   none              — drop everything (silent)
//
// Redaction mirrors src/audit.ts: any key in ALWAYS_REDACT (case-insensitive)
// or a @sensitive-tagged field is replaced with "[REDACTED]".

